data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a spacious 0.47-acre lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The well-designed layout features three comfortable bedrooms, providing ample space for rest and relaxation.    The two bathrooms are thoughtfully appointed, offering convenience and modern amenities. The heart of the home is a well-equipped kitchen, perfect for preparing delicious meals and entertaining guests. The living spaces seamlessly flow, creating a perfect balance between comfort and functionality.    Step outside to the  backyard, where you'll discover a private oasis. The generous 0.47-acre lot provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of nature. Whether you're looking for a place to call home or a peaceful retreat, this property offers the best of both worlds.    Conveniently located, this home provides easy access to to the town of Liberty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property on 0.47 acres your new home. Schedule a viewing today and imagine the possibilities!
